\v 4 And I said "I will reveal your ear saying, Take possession' before the ones who are sitting and before the elders of my people. If you will redeem, redeem. But if you will not redeem, tell me and I will know because there is no one to redeem except\f + \ft BDB 265\f* you and I am after you."
\p And he said, "I will redeem."
